    <item>
      <title>韩国调查小组寻求对尹永哲提起戒严诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-korea-probe-team-seeks-indictment-of-yoon-over-martial-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国反腐败机构结束了对总统尹锡烈有关其不幸的戒严令的初步调查，并要求检察官以叛乱罪名起诉这位被弹劾的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-korea-probe-team-seeks-indictment-of-yoon-over-martial-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 04:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔视加沙为调解其他冲突的跳板</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/qatar-sees-gaza-role-as-springboard-to-brokering-other-conflicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔成功促成了期待已久的加沙停火，提升了其作为国际调解人的声誉，其官员目前正在考虑他们还能帮助解决哪些其他冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/qatar-sees-gaza-role-as-springboard-to-brokering-other-conflicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部备忘录警告员工 DEI 计划可能带来“不良后果”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/doj-memo-warns-staff-of-adverse-consequences-over-dei-programs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继唐纳德·特朗普总统决定取消联邦政府范围内的多元化与包容性计划后，美国司法部代理负责人威胁员工，如果员工未能报告多元化与包容性计划，将面临“不利后果”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/doj-memo-warns-staff-of-adverse-consequences-over-dei-programs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 03:47:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提议由各州而非联邦紧急事务管理局负责应急响应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-floats-states-not-fema-handle-emergency-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普在前往北卡罗来纳州调查洪水灾害和加利福尼亚州山火情况之前，提议将灾难援助转交给各州自行分配，而不是由联邦紧急事务管理局做出响应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-floats-states-not-fema-handle-emergency-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 03:34:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普淡化中国利用 TikTok 监视美国人的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-downplays-threat-of-china-using-tiktok-to-spy-on-americans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周三在接受福克斯新闻采访时淡化了 TikTok 带来的国家安全风险。几天前，特朗普曾表示，不会对这款社交视频应用实施强制关闭的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-downplays-threat-of-china-using-tiktok-to-spy-on-americans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 03:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥在南海问题上抨击北京，承诺与亚洲盟友合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥在任职初期与菲律宾和印尼外长讨论南海争议水域问题时，批评北京在南海采取了“危险和破坏稳定”的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国迎来东南亚首例同性婚姻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/thailand-to-celebrate-southeast-asia-s-first-same-sex-marriages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，数百对 LGBTQ 情侣在泰国合法结婚，泰国成为东南亚第一个保障同性伴侣平等婚姻权利的国家，这一天具有历史意义。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/thailand-to-celebrate-southeast-asia-s-first-same-sex-marriages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
